com.b2international.snowowl.core.events

Class DelegatingRequest<C extends ServiceProvider,T extends ServiceProvider,R>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.b2international.snowowl.core.events.DelegatingRequest<C,T,R>
  • Type Parameters:
    C - - the required context type for this Request
    T - - the required context type of the delegate Request
    R - - the type of the result
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Request<C,R>, java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BranchRequest, HealthCheckingRequest, IndexReadRequest, MeteredRequest, RepositoryRequest, RevisionIndexReadRequest

    public abstract class DelegatingRequest<C extends ServiceProvider,T extends ServiceProvider,R>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Request<C,R>
    Delegates execution of a Request. Can be used to decorate/wrap the incoming context within another context to meet the requirements of the next Request in the execution chain, or you can use it to decorate the execution of the request chain with additional functionality like logging, execution time measurement, authorization, authentication, etc.
    Since:
    4.5
    See Also:
